    <h1 style="color: #7a3e00; font-size: 36px;">Welcome to My Laser Engraving Website</h1>

    <p style="font-size: 18px;">
        This website is about laser engraving and why I think it is such a creative and useful skill.
        Laser engraving can turn simple items into something personal, meaningful, and custom made.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px;">
        People use laser engraving for gifts, business items, signs, cups, wood projects, leather goods,
        and many other things. I like that it mixes technology with creativity.
    </p>

